snippet.title: Big Bash Boom announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Switch and PC!

For more information in the lead-up to summer's hottest game, follow the Big Bash Boom Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/Big-Bash-Boom-236003770402962/

Fully licensed with all your favourite Big Bash heroes, teams, and mascots, Big Bash Boom is this summer’s arcade blast for the whole family!
